snippet.title: Viscera Cleanup Detail: v1.0 Launch
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/246900
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/p/visceracleanupdetail_storefront
Website: http://www.runestorm.com/viscera

At last! V1.0 of VCD is out now! It's come a long way since it's early 10-day prototype. A dozen maps (plus the original legacy 4), various tools, challenges and mess to discover. Pull up your boots and grab your mop; it's a big mess, but somebody's gotta clean up!
